===第二次薩摩亞內戰與圍攻阿皮亞(1898~1899年)===
[[第二次薩摩亞內戰|第二次薩摩亞內戰]]是1898年[[德|德]]、[[英|英]]、[[美|美]]三國為了[[薩摩亞島鏈|薩摩亞島鏈]]的控制權而引發的衝突。戰爭結束於1899年的三方會議後，[[美國|美國]]獲得東半部（今[[美屬薩摩亞|美屬薩摩亞]]），[[德國|德國]]取得西半部（今[[薩摩亞|薩摩亞]]），而[[英國|英國]]獲得其它原為德屬的太平洋島鏈。<ref>Ryden, George Herbert. ''The Foreign Policy of the United States in Relation to Samoa''. New York: Octagon Books, 1975. (Reprint by special arrangement with Yale University Press. Originally published at New Haven: Yale University Press, 1928), p. 574; the Tripartite Convention (United States, Germany, Great Britain) was signed at Washington on 2 December 1899 with ratifications exchanged on 16 February 1900.(英文)</ref>

